<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Access Your eSIM Order</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e3a8a 0%, #3b82f6 100%); padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;">
    <h1 style="color: white; margin: 0; font-size: 28px;">Access Your eSIM Order</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-top: none;">
    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Hello,</p>
    
    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      You requested access to your eSIM order. Click the button below to view your order details and eSIM information.
    </p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
      <a href="{{accessUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background: #3b82f6; color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">
        View My Order
      </a>
    </div>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
      <strong>Order ID:</strong> {{orderId}}
    </p>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      This link will expire in {{expiresIn}}. If you didn't request this link, you can safely ignore this email.
    </p>
    
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
      <a href="{{accessUrl}}" style="color: #3b82f6; word-break: break-all;">{{accessUrl}}</a>
    </p>
  </div>
  
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px;">
    <p>Â© Voyage eSIM. All rights reserved.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

